&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage handoff from sales to service and onboarding process&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure accurate setup in AMS/CRM and clear client communication&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Carrier &amp;amp; Internal Collaboration&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with carrier partners on service-related matters&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Align with producers on account strategy and renewals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support cross-sell and operational initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
